data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 2 story home in White City. This home is 2080 sq ft with 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. The kitchen is exceptionally large with lots of storage, a pantry and lots of countertop space with an eating bar. It has tile floors with stainless appliances including the refrigerator. The living room has Laminate flooring and a custom-made wood plank built-in for your TV. The primary suite is on the main level. Upstairs has an extra-large bedroom with 2 large walk-in closets, 2 additional bedrooms, a full bathroom and the laundry area with built-in shelves. The back yard is fully fenced, has a nice patio area and a storage shed.
